      <title>达里奥的继任者在桥水基金的成绩好坏参半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/dalio-s-successor-gets-mixed-report-card-at-bridgewater-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社的凯瑟琳·伯顿报道，桥水基金首席执行官尼尔·巴尔·德亚(Nir Bar Dea)在雷·达里奥(Ray Dalio)领导下多年回报平平后，正在努力保持投资者的信任，同时也在重塑一些员工认为已经变得压抑的企业文化。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/dalio-s-successor-gets-mixed-report-card-at-bridgewater-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 17:27:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛的 Wilson-Elizondo 谈模型投资组合的受欢迎程度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/goldman-sachs-wilson-elizondo-on-the-model-portfolio-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着模型投资组合越来越受欢迎，高盛资产管理多资产解决方案联合首席信息官 Alexandra Wilson-Elizondo 与 Scarlet Fu 和 Katie Greifeld 一起解释了模型投资组合的日益流行以及 ETF 如何利用这一机会。她在“彭博 ETF IQ”上发表演讲。

 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/goldman-sachs-wilson-elizondo-on-the-model-portfolio-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 17:22:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据显示，美联储银行借款计划“太好了，不容错过”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/fed-bank-borrowing-program-was-too-good-to-pass-up-data-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 Wrightson ICAP 对上周发布的数据的分析，美联储旧金山地区的银行带领机构在 1 月份加大了对一项关键工具的使用，因为它们利用了慷慨借贷成本的最后窗口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/fed-bank-borrowing-program-was-too-good-to-pass-up-data-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 17:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约大学必须提高入学率或出售大楼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/new-york-college-must-boost-enrollment-or-lose-astoria-building</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约沃恩航空技术学院与其市政债券持有人达成协议，要求其在秋季学期之前增加更多学生，否则必须出售位于阿斯托里亚的一栋培训大楼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/new-york-college-must-boost-enrollment-or-lose-astoria-building</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 17:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据导致日元走弱，日本外汇干预风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/yen-weakens-on-us-data-raising-risk-of-japanese-fx-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑美元汇率正在跌向 152 日元，这是交易员认为日本官员干预市场的风险上升的关键水平，因为强劲的美国工厂数据提振了美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/yen-weakens-on-us-data-raising-risk-of-japanese-fx-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:44:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据显示，由于流动性稀薄，新兴市场资产小幅走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/emerging-assets-edge-lower-amid-thin-liquidity-us-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国公布最新数据后，由于欧洲、澳大利亚和香港的多个市场周一因复活节休市，全球流动性依然稀薄，新兴市场资产周一扩大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/emerging-assets-edge-lower-amid-thin-liquidity-us-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 14:12:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油价格因需求增长和大中东战争的潜力而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明今年的需求可能强于预期，而以色列对叙利亚的袭击可能会扩大中东冲突，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 23:23:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美联储降息押注逐渐消退，股市跟随债券下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/asian-stocks-set-to-gain-as-fed-awaits-more-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可靠的美国工厂数据强化了美联储将不急于降息的猜测，全球最大的债券市场面临压力，股市回吐涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/asian-stocks-set-to-gain-as-fed-awaits-more-data-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 22:04:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数十亿美元涌入活跃 ETF 寻找廉价新兴市场股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/billions-flood-active-etfs-in-hunt-for-cheap-developing-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者在全球范围内寻找被低估的股票，一个越来越受欢迎的目的地是专注于新兴市场的主动管理型交易所交易基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/billions-flood-active-etfs-in-hunt-for-cheap-developing-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因地雷争端，惠誉将巴拿马信用评级下调至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/panama-cut-to-junk-by-fitch-amid-mine-spat-bonds-slide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级取消了巴拿马的投资级信用评级，因为去年一个重要铜矿的关闭加剧了该国的财政担忧和破坏增长前景的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/panama-cut-to-junk-by-fitch-amid-mine-spat-bonds-slide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 17:06:01 GMT</pubDate>
